{"tid":1563623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（警世）不要睇小藍絲活動","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:09.000Z","uid":278154,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b237017e7edca9ba894856bb305c69a52b753aa","tid":1563623,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"今日IFC有藍絲唱國歌，可能你會笑收錢，大陸人黎，一定唔夠我地咁多人，但我聽到有藍絲睇完IFC講：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">原來香港人都咁愛國</span></strong></span><br />\n因為佢地根本唔會了解件事由來，只會睇到結果，如果黎緊再有更多類似嘅活動，係會令到藍絲激活起來，當你見到越來越藍絲捉跳閘、撕連儂牆、唱國歌....就會令到更多藍絲越來越囂張，你知佢哋多數好暴力，只會用道德高地去同你講，有時我地d學生哥經驗唔夠，比人拍片屌，唔好睇小，好多藍絲group討論，加上我地文宣越來越少，係社區戰好易失守。<br />\n不要輕敵，圍爐取暖，亦要思考內憂外患！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3ef07317de40f3a489e49f02e73aec8a4885f90b","tid":1563623,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:55:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"35c5de16ccf04fef336b2a66caef577812187001","tid":1563623,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"就輸啦"},{"pid":"c23becf2df194c29a17908e646ddb82d5b586413","tid":1563623,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"最怕真心藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e201aa90d30a2bcbaf51bea746c2da26df4e23","tid":1563623,"uid":141833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f73c211c8e26965972c9bf87932a715aefcae9c","tid":1563623,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DATbH2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDATbH2o.jpg&h=de14d781&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dae3314c8ed5c446637ba5bfc743a66fcc53aa90","tid":1563623,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"5fe3a8a8a48adc37322338704cead49bb468be9b","tid":1563623,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"唔可以只等人權法案通過，如果到時咩事都冇發生，影響唔到香港，我哋會輸得好慘，自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"f983ca8dcb372005196ec403f821310387f3a626","tid":1563623,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"推到有人理"}]}